These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, social-worker, designer, mechanic, musician, bartender, entrepreneur
There are 7 different nationalities: brazilian, british, chinese, colombian, indonesian, nigerian, spanish
 1. the chinese is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 2. the chinese is on the right of the indonesian##1
 3. the chinese is on the left or right of the designer##3
 4. the spanish is the accountant##1
 5. the british is the mechanic##1
 6. the brazilian is in the middle##1
 7. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the designer is in an even position##4
 9. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
10. the nigerian is on the left or right of the spanish##3
11. the accountant is on the right of the nigerian##1
12. the designer is the indonesian##1
13. the entrepreneur is on the right of the bartender##1
14. the musician is on the left or right of the designer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |    7    |
| Job   | musician      | designer      | bartender    | entrepreneur    | social-worker | accountant     | mechanic     |
| Nationality   | colombian | indonesian | chinese | brazilian | nigerian   | spanish | british |

