.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: chinese, pakistani, american, russian, argentine, spanish, colombian
7 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, goat, hamster, hedgehog, pony, rat
 1. the american is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
 2. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the russian##3
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
 4. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 5. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the owner of the pony is the russian##1
 7. the pakistani is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the spanish is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 9. the russian is the owner of the pony##1
10. the american is between the owner of the pony and the pakistani##2
11. the spanish is in the middle##1
12. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
13. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3
14. the colombian is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |    3    |     4      |      5      |     6     |   7    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | american | russian | spanish   | colombian | chinese | argentine |
| Pet           | hedgehog | cat          | pony    | chinchilla | hamster     | goat      | rat    |

