.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: august, may, september, december, march, april, january
The people have 7 different jobs:  firefighter, journalist, nurse, paramedic, police-officer, project-manager, teacher
 1. the nurse is on the right of the teacher##1
 2. the teacher is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in december##2
 5. the project-manager is on the left or right of the journalist##3
 6. the nurse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
 8. the firefighter is on the far left##1
 9. the journalist is the person who's birthday is in august##1
10. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
11. the project-manager is the person who's birthday is in january##1
12. the police-officer is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in january##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |       5        |        6        |     7      |
| Birthday   | december        | may  | april | september | march           | january           | august  |
| Job    | firefighter | paramedic | teacher   | nurse    | police-officer | project-manager | journalist |

