.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-4::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, dancing, photography, puzzles, reading, woodworking
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: zombie, satire, musical, horror, thriller, time-travel, family
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
 3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the person watching family movies is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
 7. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
11. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
12. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
13. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4      |      5       |      6      |      7      |
| Hobby   | dancing | reading    | photography | card-games | puzzles      | board-games | woodworking |
| Movie-Genre     | family  | zombie | horror   | musical  | time-travel | thriller     | satire    |

