 3. the fan of r&b is between the fan of d&b and the craftsman house##2
 4. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
 5. the ranch-style house is between the colonial house and the craftsman house##2
 6. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
 7. the cottage house is the fan of jazz##1
 8. the wooden house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
 9. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
