 3. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
 4. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
 5. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
 7. the fan of indie is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the fan of rock is the bongani-smoker##1
 9. the fonseca-smoker is in an even position##4
10. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
11. the bongani-smoker is in the middle##1
12. the ritmeester-smoker is the fan of pop##1
13. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
