.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-20::.
7 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, dog, horse, hamster, chinchilla, turtle
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, disco, dubstep, gospel, hip-hop, metal, punk
 1. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 3. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
 4. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the horse is the fan of disco##1
 6. the fan of d&b is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 7. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the fan of punk##1
11. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
12. the fan of disco is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |   5    |      6      |    7     |
| Pet          | chinchilla   | dog | turtle | goldfish | hamster | mouse | horse |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | punk      | metal     | dubstep  | gospel | d&b         | disco    |

 